results.name: Decimal expansion of a constant related to A255360.
formula: Equals 2^(5/4)*Pi^(5/4)*exp(137/3024 - 5*Zeta'(-5)) * Product_{n>=1} ((n^5)! / stirling(n^5)), where stirling(n^5) = sqrt(2*Pi) * n^(5*n^5 + 5/2) / exp(n^5) is the Stirling approximation of (n^5)! and Zeta'(-5) = A259070. - _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Apr 20 2016
results.author: _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Feb 24 2015
